name: Help I'm LOST in the woods
name_original: Help I'm LOST in the woods
description:
Hello!

My name is Eugene  I am just getting in to making games. I joined GDU online to help me along the way. Ive been working on this game here and there so I made a bet with myself that I would publish this game before the end of the year. With 1 hour to spare... here it is. Help I'm LOST in the woods! In the game just explore the beautiful environment I created. I know I have a lot to improve on but If anyone can give me constrictive criticism that will be great. I'm looking to learn! Do not hold back.
